                        "version": 0,
                        "content": "The nurse overhears the primary health care provider (PHCP) tell a client with rheumatoid arthritis that the condition needs to be treated with gold therapy. The nurse interprets that the PHCP is referring to which medication?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "80db17ea97ed8fdcd1b6b9666390fca1",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Applying 应用",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nAuranofin is a gold preparation used to manage rheumatoid arthritis in clients with insufficient therapeutic response to nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory drugs. Prednisone is a corticosteroid. Pentostatin and fludarabine phosphate are antineoplastic agents.\n\nTest-Taking Strategy:\nEliminate pentostatin and fludarabine phosphate first because they are comparable or alike and are both antineoplastic agents. Regarding the remaining choices, recalling that prednisone is a corticosteroid will direct you to the correct option.",
                        "id": "cc0a46c436c140f09ef1e5b42e4d1426",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "e7e31bde58674dbc84cac933284544b7",
                                "content": "The injection site for itching and edema"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "1e5dcc6749374d529bcb0813da183e76",
                                "content": "The white blood cell counts and platelet counts"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "d9cd85f375b047c494f767568403909e",
                                "content": "Whether the client is experiencing fatigue and joint pain"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "e68ac7c7fc5949cdad01e66259a17a56",
                                "content": "Whether the client is experiencing a metallic taste in the mouth and a loss of appetite"
                            }
                        ],
                        "extJson": {
                            "optionList": [
                                {
                                    "isRight": "0",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "e7e31bde58674dbc84cac933284544b7",
                                    "content": "The injection site for itching and edema"
                                },
                                {
                                    "isRight": "1",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "1e5dcc6749374d529bcb0813da183e76",
                                    "content": "The white blood cell counts and platelet counts"
                                },
                                {
                                    "isRight": "0",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "d9cd85f375b047c494f767568403909e",
                                    "content": "Whether the client is experiencing fatigue and joint pain"
                                },
                                {
                                    "isRight": "0",
                                    "userAnswer": "",
                                    "isSelected": "0",
                                    "id": "e68ac7c7fc5949cdad01e66259a17a56",
                                    "content": "Whether the client is experiencing a metallic taste in the mouth and a loss of appetite"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
